  "prompt": "What are some songs which include underwater sounds?",
  "response": "Here are some songs that include underwater sounds or are themed around underwater environments:\n\n1. **\"Under the Sea\" - Samuel E. Wright (from *The Little Mermaid*)**  \n   - This classic Disney song features oceanic themes and the sounds of underwater life, making it a perfect fit.\n\n2. **\"Oceanic Feeling\" - Lorde**  \n   - Lorde's song from her album *Solar Power* incorporates ambient sounds that evoke the ocean and underwater vibes.\n\n3. **\"Aquatic\" - BLOND:ISH**  \n   - This deep house track includes underwater soundscapes and whale sounds, creating a serene, oceanic atmosphere.\n\n4. **\"Underwater\" - R\u00dcF\u00dcS DU SOL**  \n   - This electronic track features aquatic synths and a submerged, ethereal soundscape.\n\n5. **\"Breathe\" - Telepopmusik**  \n   - While not explicitly about water, this track has a flowing, liquid-like quality in its production that can evoke underwater imagery.\n\n6. **\"Porpoise Song\" - The Monkees**  \n   - This psychedelic track from the late 1960s includes echoey, underwater-like effects and a dreamy, oceanic vibe.\n\n7. **\"Deep Sea Diver\" - Metric**  \n   - This song incorporates watery, atmospheric sounds that fit its title and theme.\n\n8. **\"Submarine\" - Alex Turner (from *Submarine* EP)**  \n   - This acoustic track by the Arctic Monkeys frontman has a mellow, reflective tone that complements its submarine theme.\n\n9. **\"Ocean\" - Lady A**  \n   - While not directly featuring underwater sounds, this song uses oceanic imagery to create a watery, emotional atmosphere.\n\n10. **\"Atlantis\" - Donovan**  \n    - This folk-rock classic features oceanic themes and a mystical underwater vibe.\n\nThese songs use either literal underwater sounds or atmospheric production to evoke the feeling of being underwater or surrounded by water. Let me know if you'd like more recommendations!",
